<p>=E2=87=92 Area of a hexagon=3D $\frac{(=E2=88=9A(3 )\: x 36\: x\: 36}{24=
}$&nbsp;=3D 93.528 sq. cm</p>



<p>Let us see how to use the hexagon calculator for finding the area using =
